+
+#### test_plan
+- `tests/test_vault_rotation.py::test_import_sets_ttl_once` — patch
+  `vault.set_default_ttl`, import `src.lib.vault`, assert called with
+  `seconds=300`.
+- `tests/test_vault_rotation.py::test_old_secret_valid_for_window` —
+  rotate, advance clock 299s, assert `secret(name)` returns prior value;
+  advance to 301s, assert returns new value. Catches a wall-clock
+  off-by-one.
